</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Problematično područje
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0100: Krug &#34;A&#34; masenog ili volumenskog protoka zraka
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Izlazni napon kruga signala MAF senzora viši je od 0,5 V čak i kada je napajanje MAF senzora isključeno.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(logika detekcije 3 ciklusa vožnje, ali MIL ne zasvijetli)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
MAF senzor i/ili njegov krug
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0102: Niski napon kruga &#34;A&#34; masenog ili volumenskog protoka zraka
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Izlazni napon kruga signala MAF senzora niži je od 0,02 V tijekom 5 sekundi.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(logika detekcije 3 ciklusa vožnje)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0103: Visoki napon kruga &#34;A&#34; masenog ili volumenskog protoka zraka
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Izlazni napon kruga signala MAF senzora viši je od 4,74 V tijekom 5 sekundi.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(logika detekcije 3 ciklusa vožnje)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
